---
import ServiceLayout from '../../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Microservices & Containerization"
  description="Modern application architecture with microservices and container orchestration"
>
  <div class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Container Solutions</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Container Services</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• Docker containerization</li>
          <li>• Kubernetes orchestration</li>
          <li>• Container security</li>
          <li>• Image optimization</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Microservices</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• Service decomposition</li>
          <li>• API gateway design</li>
          <li>• Service mesh</li>
          <li>• Event-driven architecture</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">DevSecOps</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• CI/CD pipelines</li>
          <li>• Security scanning</li>
          <li>• Compliance automation</li>
          <li>• Monitoring & logging</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-indigo-100 p-8 rounded-lg mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Container Platforms</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <img src="https://kubernetes.io/images/favicon.png" alt="Kubernetes" class="w-16 h-16 mb-4">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Kubernetes</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• Cluster management</li>
          <li>• Auto-scaling</li>
          <li>• Load balancing</li>
          <li>• Service discovery</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <img src="https://www.docker.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/cropped-Docker-favicon-32x32.png" alt="Docker" class="w-16 h-16 mb-4">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Docker</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• Container builds</li>
          <li>• Image management</li>
          <li>• Compose services</li>
          <li>• Network isolation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <img src="https://istio.io/favicons/favicon-32x32.png" alt="Istio" class="w-16 h-16 mb-4">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Service Mesh</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• Traffic management</li>
          <li>• Security policies</li>
          <li>• Observability</li>
          <li>• Service resilience</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Microservices Architecture</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Design Patterns</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">API Gateway</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Centralized API management and routing</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Event Sourcing</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Event-driven state management</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">CQRS</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Command and query responsibility segregation</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Best Practices</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Domain-Driven Design</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Business-aligned service boundaries</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Circuit Breakers</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Fault tolerance and resilience</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Distributed Tracing</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">End-to-end request monitoring</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-purple-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Modernize Your Applications</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">Ready to transform your monolithic applications into scalable microservices? Let's discuss your containerization strategy.</p>
    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors">
        Start Your Transformation
      </a>
      <a href="/services/cloud/analytics" class="inline-block bg-white text-purple-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors">
        Explore Analytics Services
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>